he dream changes from unrealized to realized/true.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs16\lang1024\i0\b0 Note also that the string {\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i come }is present in English {\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i become}, and {\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i venir} \'91come\'92 is found in French {\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i devenir} \'91become\'92 and several Romance cognates.}}}
